HEADWORD: Glutamic
<hw>Glu*tam"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Glut</ets>en
+ <ets>-amic</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to
